        Buying and Selling at the Same Time in Brisbane: Managing Simultaneous Settlements
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Coordinating a sale and a purchase so they settle at the same time is achievable, but it requires planning and clear communication between all parties. Here is how to approach it.
      </p>
